short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Set custom html for the New Tab.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Homeprint let's you create your own html which will override the default html for the "New Tab" page. The HTML will be synced to your Google Chrome account automatically so any other computer you have the extension installed on will share the same home page.

Ways to use it:
    - Overwhelmed by bookmarks? Create your own "dashboard" of links using whatever style and format matches your workflow.

HTML size is limited by Chrome's sync API to 8KB.
